Title: Wonder Woman
Writer: William Moulton Marston (characters), Gail Simone (story), Michael Jelenic (story), Michael Jelenic (screenplay)
Actors: Keri Russell, Nathan Fillion, Alfred Molina, Rosario Dawson
Plot: A modern man's trespass of the island of the Amazons enables an imprisoned war god to escape and Princess Diana wins the responsibility to recapture him.
